snippet.title: A Place, Forbidden Trailer
snippet.description:
The Library of Ouroboros. It exists in many places at once - and none of them at all. Few claim to have seen it. All who have speak of vast tracts of tomes, each alone containing knowledge powerful - and horrible - enough to transform a person into something beyond mortality. None who speak its name are entirely sound of mind.

It is open to the public, for free, in the following segments of reality:
itch.io: https://banzaibonsai.itch.io/a-place-forbidden
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1333920/A_Place_Forbidden/

You may follow news on the Library updates at the following page: https://twitter.com/BustedKeyboards

We hope you enjoy your visit.
